Here I will list the req for our project

Problem:
Hard way to start to make a business with low amount of money 

Solution: 
A platform to give a chance for everyone and small entrepreneurs 

Requirements:
1. A platform to start the business 
2. A fast way to start 
3. Easy to pay & receive software
4. Friendly user interface 
5. Keep track of purchased items to recommend similar items for the user
6. Advertisement deals for anyone that want to sell faster
7. Support feature 
8. Different items for different countries 
9. Many delivery options 
10. Service option as an item 
11. Renting service  
12. Unlimited option for posting for example, programing service, renting a car.
13. Insure security and privacy 
